<body>
    <h1>setup and generate steaming avater</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"e7063b1314bf">
<li local-id=3D"032891994e8d">
<p local-id=3D"003f49e78ef3">Go to the server has a 4090 gpu</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0fc647821c47">
<p local-id=3D"54ee1b843847">Install conda</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">wget ht=
tps://repo.anaconda.com/miniconda/Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh
bash Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh
source ~/.bashrc</pre>
</div>
</div></li>
<li local-id=3D"8e8a5d29c513">
<p local-id=3D"4c3c47acb4b7">Create and activate conda virtual env</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">conda c=
reate -n flashhead python=3D3.10
conda activate flashhead</pre>
</div>
</div></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"cfd7870fce8c">4. Install pytorch</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">pip ins=
tall torch=3D=3D2.7.1 torchvision=3D=3D0.22.1 --index-url https://download.=
pytorch.org/whl/cu128</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"d30273bcb433"></p>
<ol start=3D"5" local-id=3D"7ed5f34487ab">
<li local-id=3D"c575739a1e64">
<p local-id=3D"92733ba972b2">Download soulx-flashhead_1.3B</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">git clo=
ne https://github.com/Soul-AILab/SoulX-FlashHead.git
cd SoulX-FlashHead</pre>
</div>
</div></li>
<li local-id=3D"8377564f599c">
<p local-id=3D"34d22f369bb1">Install dependencies</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">pip ins=
tall -r requirements.txt
pip install ninja
pip install flash_attn=3D=3D2.8.0.post2 --no-build-isolation
pip install sageattention=3D=3D1.0.6 --no-build-isolation</pre>
</div>
</div></li>
<li local-id=3D"b9a7fd935733">
<p local-id=3D"cc0719e76f22">Install FFmpeg</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">conda i=
nstall -c conda-forge ffmpeg=3D=3D7</pre>
</div>
</div></li>
<li local-id=3D"477734dda478">
<p local-id=3D"ace871a2dc71">install model</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">pip ins=
tall "huggingface_hub[cli]"
hf download Soul-AILab/SoulX-FlashHead-1_3B --local-dir ./models/SoulX-Flas=
hHead-1_3B
hf download facebook/wav2vec2-base-960h --local-dir ./models/wav2vec2-base-=
960h</pre>
</div>
</div></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"421d4fa12ed9">9. run script to generate stream video</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence"># Infer=
 with [Lite-Model] on single GPU
bash inference_script_single_gpu_lite.sh
# Real-time inference speed can be supported on single RTX-4090 (up to 3 co=
ncurrent).</pre>
</div>
</div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
